---
// Experience section component
---

<section id="experiencia" class="experience-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header fade-in">
			<h2 class="section-title gradient-text" data-en="Work experience" data-es="Experiencia laboral">Experiencia laboral</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle" data-en="My professional journey" data-es="Mi trayectoria profesional">Mi trayectoria profesional</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="experience-container">
			<div class="experience-card slide-in-up" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
				<div class="card-header">
					<div class="company-logo">
						<div class="logo-placeholder">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
								<path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="job-info">
						<h3 class="job-title" data-en="Junior Researcher" data-es="Investigador junior">Investigador junior</h3>
						<div class="company-name">Odin Solutions</div>
						<div class="job-period" data-en="February 2023 - Present" data-es="Febrero 2023 - Presente">Febrero 2023 - Presente</div>
					</div>
					<div class="status-badge">
						<span class="status-dot"></span>
						<span data-en="Current" data-es="Actual">Actual</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="card-content">
					<p class="job-description" data-en="Participation in European and national projects (MASTERPIECE, 6G-PATH, UniMaaS, NINEMO, MAS4Care, EDS4Agro), designing and developing backend solutions with Python, Java, Go, and Node-RED. Experience with REST APIs, microservices architecture, authentication systems (Keycloak), and containerized deployments in Docker/Kubernetes. Management of CI/CD pipelines with Jenkins and Git, plus administration of internal services ensuring high availability and security." data-es="Participación en proyectos europeos y nacionales (MASTERPIECE, 6G-PATH, UniMaaS, NINEMO, MAS4Care, EDS4Agro), diseñando y desarrollando soluciones backend con Python, Java, Go y Node-RED. Experiencia con APIs REST, arquitectura de microservicios, sistemas de autenticación (Keycloak) y despliegues contenedorizados en Docker/Kubernetes. Gestión de pipelines CI/CD con Jenkins y Git, además de administración de servicios internos garantizando alta disponibilidad y seguridad.">Participación en proyectos europeos y nacionales (MASTERPIECE, 6G-PATH, UniMaaS, NINEMO, MAS4Care, EDS4Agro), diseñando y desarrollando soluciones backend con Python, Java, Go y Node-RED. Experiencia con APIs REST, arquitectura de microservicios, sistemas de autenticación (Keycloak) y despliegues contenedorizados en Docker/Kubernetes. Gestión de pipelines CI/CD con Jenkins y Git, además de administración de servicios internos garantizando alta disponibilidad y seguridad.</p>
					
					<div class="achievements-grid">
						<div class="achievement-item">
							<div class="achievement-icon">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M12 1L3 5V11C3 16.55 6.84 21.74 12 23C17.16 21.74 21 16.55 21 11V5L12 1M12 7C13.4 7 14.8 8.6 14.8 10V11.5C15.4 11.5 16 12.1 16 12.7V16.2C16 16.8 15.4 17.3 14.8 17.3H9.2C8.6 17.3 8 16.8 8 16.2V12.7C8 12.1 8.6 11.5 9.2 11.5V10C9.2 8.6 10.6 7 12 7M12 8.2C11.2 8.2 10.5 8.7 10.5 10V11.5H13.5V10C13.5 8.7 12.8 8.2 12 8.2Z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<p data-en="Design and development from scratch of a Policy Administration Point (PAP) integrating XACML with Flask in Python, containerized in Docker and used in the European MASTERPIECE project." data-es="Diseño y desarrollo desde cero de un Punto de Administración de Políticas (PAP) integrando XACML con Flask en Python, contenedorizado en Docker y usado en el proyecto europeo MASTERPIECE.">Diseño y desarrollo desde cero de un Punto de Administración de Políticas (PAP) integrando XACML con Flask en Python, contenedorizado en Docker y usado en el proyecto europeo MASTERPIECE.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="achievement-item">
							<div class="achievement-icon">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4M12,6A6,6 0 0,0 6,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,18A6,6 0 0,0 18,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,6M12,8A4,4 0 0,1 16,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,16A4,4 0 0,1 8,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,8M12,10A2,2 0 0,0 10,12A2,2 0 0,0 12,14A2,2 0 0,0 14,12A2,2 0 0,0 12,10Z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<p data-en="Development of an MQTT LoRaWAN agent for decoding device data and normalization to NGSI-LD and NGSIv2 for publication in Orion-LD. This IoT agent achieves 46% less average resource consumption compared to the average of open source agents." data-es="Desarrollo de un agente MQTT LoRaWAN para decodificación de datos de dispositivos de la empresa y normalización a NGSI-LD y NGSIv2 para su publicación en Orion-LD. Este agente IoT consigue un 46% menos de consumo medio de recursos frente a la media de agentes de código abierto.">Desarrollo de un agente MQTT LoRaWAN para decodificación de datos de dispositivos de la empresa y normalización a NGSI-LD y NGSIv2 para su publicación en Orion-LD. Este agente IoT consigue un 46% menos de consumo medio de recursos frente a la media de agentes de código abierto.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="achievement-item">
							<div class="achievement-icon">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M12,3C7.58,3 4,4.79 4,7C4,9.21 7.58,11 12,11C16.42,11 20,9.21 20,7C20,4.79 16.42,3 12,3M4,9V12C4,14.21 7.58,16 12,16C16.42,16 20,14.21 20,12V9C20,11.21 16.42,13 12,13C7.58,13 4,11.21 4,9M4,14V17C4,19.21 7.58,21 12,21C16.42,21 20,19.21 20,17V14C20,16.21 16.42,18 12,18C7.58,18 4,16.21 4,14Z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<p data-en="Design and development of a notification ingestion service from Orion-LD (MongoDB) for data storage in Elasticsearch/InfluxDB, and implementation of an API to retrieve, transform and expose data in NGSI-LD and NGSIv2, adapted to company needs. Solution used and extended in the European MASTERPIECE project." data-es="Diseño y desarrollo de un servicio de ingesta de notificaciones de Orion-LD (MongoDB) para el almacenamiento de datos en Elasticsearch/InfluxDB, e implementación de una API para recuperar, transformar y exponer los datos en NGSI-LD y NGSIv2, adaptado a las necesidades de la empresa. Solución usada y extendida en el proyecto europeo MASTERPIECE.">Diseño y desarrollo de un servicio de ingesta de notificaciones de Orion-LD (MongoDB) para el almacenamiento de datos en Elasticsearch/InfluxDB, e implementación de una API para recuperar, transformar y exponer los datos en NGSI-LD y NGSIv2, adaptado a las necesidades de la empresa. Solución usada y extendida en el proyecto europeo MASTERPIECE.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="tech-stack">
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="Backend & APIs" data-es="Backend & APIs">Backend & APIs</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Flask</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Java</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Go</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Node-RED</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Groovy</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">REST APIs</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">OpenAPI</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Hyperledger Fabric</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="Security & Authentication" data-es="Seguridad & Autenticación">Seguridad & Autenticación</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">XACML</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Keycloak</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="Databases" data-es="Bases de datos">Bases de datos</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">MongoDB</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">InfluxDB</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Elasticsearch</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="DevOps & Infrastructure" data-es="DevOps & Infraestructura">DevOps & Infraestructura</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Kubernetes</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">NGINX</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Traefik</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Bash</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Jenkins</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Git/GitHub/GitLab</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="IoT & Data Processing" data-es="IoT & Procesamiento de Datos">IoT & Procesamiento de Datos</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">LoRaWAN</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">FIWARE</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">NGSI-LD</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Orion-LD</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="Frontend" data-es="Frontend">Frontend</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">Vue.js</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">HTML/CSS</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tech-category">
							<span class="category-label" data-en="Tools" data-es="Herramientas">Herramientas</span>
							<div class="tech-tags">
								<span class="tech-tag">Grafana</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">Overleaf</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">DokuWiki</span>
								<span class="tech-tag">ChartMuseum</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.experience-section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	
	.section-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.section-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}
	
	.experience-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}
	
	.experience-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 24px;
		padding: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
		transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
	}
	
	.experience-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
		transform: scaleX(0);
		transform-origin: left;
		transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
	}
	
	.experience-card:hover::before {
		transform: scaleX(1);
	}
	
	.experience-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
	
	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding: 2rem 2rem 1rem 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.company-logo {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.logo-placeholder {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: white;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.experience-card:hover .logo-placeholder {
		transform: rotate(5deg) scale(1.05);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
	}
	
	.logo-placeholder svg {
		width: 28px;
		height: 28px;
	}
	
	.job-info {
		flex: 1;
		min-width: 0;
	}
	
	.job-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}
	
	.company-name {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-accent);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}
	
	.job-period {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		opacity: 0.8;
	}
	
	.status-badge {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #4CAF50;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}
	
	.status-dot {
		width: 6px;
		height: 6px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #4CAF50;
		animation: pulse 2s infinite;
	}
	
	@keyframes pulse {
		0%, 100% {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0.7;
			transform: scale(1.2);
		}
	}
	
	.card-content {
		padding: 0 2rem 2rem 2rem;
	}
	
	.job-description {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}
	
	.achievements-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.achievement-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-radius: 12px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.achievement-item:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
		transform: translateX(8px);
	}
	
	.achievement-icon {
		width: 24px;
		height: 24px;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		color: var(--text-accent);
		margin-top: 2px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	
	.achievement-icon svg {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		fill: currentColor;
		stroke: none;
		display: block;
	}
	
	.achievement-item p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}
	
	.tech-stack {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	
	.tech-category {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.category-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-accent);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}
	
	.tech-tags {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.tech-tag {
		padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 16px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.tech-tag::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: -100%;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
		transition: left 0.5s ease;
	}
	
	.tech-tag:hover::before {
		left: 100%;
	}
	
	.tech-tag:hover {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
		color: white;
		border-color: transparent;
		transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.05);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.experience-container {
			padding: 0 0.5rem;
		}
		
		.card-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: 1rem;
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.status-badge {
			align-self: flex-start;
		}
		
		.card-content {
			padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.logo-placeholder {
			width: 50px;
			height: 50px;
		}
		
		.logo-placeholder svg {
			width: 24px;
			height: 24px;
		}
		
		.job-title {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
		
		.company-name {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		
		.tech-stack {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}
		
		.achievement-item {
			padding: 0.75rem;
		}
		
		.achievement-item:hover {
			transform: none;
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.experience-section {
			padding: 3rem 0.75rem;
		}
		
		.section-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.section-subtitle {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.experience-container {
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		
		.experience-card {
			padding: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			border-radius: 12px;
			overflow: hidden;
		}
		
		.card-header {
			padding: 0;
			gap: 0.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}
		
		.company-logo {
			flex-shrink: 0;
		}
		
		.logo-placeholder {
			width: 32px;
			height: 32px;
		}
		
		.job-info {
			flex: 1;
			min-width: 0;
		}
		
		.job-title {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			line-height: 1.3;
			margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
			word-wrap: break-word;
		}
		
		.company-name {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
		}
		
		.job-period {
			font-size: 0.7rem;
		}
		
		.status-badge {
			font-size: 0.7rem;
			padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
			white-space: nowrap;
		}
		
		.card-content {
			padding: 0;
		}
		
		.job-description {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			line-height: 1.5;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			text-align: justify;
		}
		
		.achievements-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 0.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}
		
		.achievement-item {
			padding: 0.75rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
		}
		
		.achievement-icon {
			width: 16px;
			height: 16px;
			flex-shrink: 0;
		}
		
		.achievement-item p {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			line-height: 1.4;
		}
		
		.tech-categories {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}
		
		.tech-category h4 {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}
		
		.tech-tags {
			gap: 0.25rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}
		
		.tech-tag {
			padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
			font-size: 0.65rem;
			border-radius: 4px;
			white-space: nowrap;
		}
	}
</style>